Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/fleet?startDate=2026-03-08&endDate=2026-03-14
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/borders?startDate=2026-03-08&endDate=2026-03-14
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Monthly Management Report
# Export all monthly reports
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export/trips?startDate=2026-03-01&endDate=2026-03-31
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export/financial?startDate=2026-03-01&endDate=2026-03-31
