###############################################################################
# ERROR HANDLING TESTS
###############################################################################

### Get Dashboard - Invalid Date Range (Should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/main?startDate=invalid&endDate=invalid
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Generate Report - Missing Dates (Should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/trips
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Export Report - Invalid Type (Should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/export/invalid?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create Notification - Missing Required Fields (Should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Missing userId"
}

### Create Bulk Notification - Empty Users (Should fail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/bulk
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userIds": [],
  "title": "Test",
  "message": "Test message"
}

### Get Notification - Invalid ID (Should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications/invalid-uuid
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Mark Notification as Read - Already Read (Should fail if already read)
POST {{baseUrl}}/notifications/{{notificationId}}/read
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Unauthorized Access (Should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/main

### Unauthorized Report Access (Should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/trips?startDate=2026-01-01&endDate=2026-12-31

### Unauthorized Notification Access (Should fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications

